References[]


Trivia[]

Pyke, the Bloodharbor Ripper
  • ▶️  "Did I 'support' right?" alludes to the conception that supports aren't allowed to take kills normally unless needed to.
  • ▶️  "What's worth more? A pound of flesh or a gallon of blood?" references Merchant of Venice, during which Shylock demands a pound of flesh from Antonio (later on, it is ruled in court that he cannot spill a drop of blood, as his contract with Antonio specifically states a pound of flesh—not blood).
  • ▶️  "I want to watch the world drown." is a play on a quote from The Dark Knight ("Some men just want to watch the world burn.")
  • ▶️  "Part of the kill, part of the gold." quotes Pirates of the Caribbean: At World's End ("Part of the crew, part of the ship.").[1]
  • Pyke is the third champion to receive ping-related voice lines, the first two being Rakan and Xayah.
PROJECT: Pyke
  • ▶️  "You get a snake! And you get a snake! Everybody gets a snake!" references The Oprah Winfrey Show.
  • ▶️  "Why are you running?!" quotes the Nigerian film Pretty Liars.
  • ▶️  "Come on out! We've got a city to burn." quotes Cyberpunk 2077.
  • ▶️  "Make me feel alive again!" quotes the enigmatic Gray Fox from Metal Gear Solid.
Empyrean Pyke
  • ▶️  "Universe is cruel. Why should I be any different?" quotes Davy Jones from Pirates of the Caribbean.
